%sql
SELECT AVG(price) price, neighbourhood, room_type
FROM airbnb
WHERE room_type = "${room=Private room,Entire home/apt|Private room|Shared room}"
GROUP BY neighbourhood, room_type
ORDER BY price DESC
LIMIT 6
